examples.en: Ben laughed loudly.
I laughed vastly.

examples.ru: Мария посмотрела на него и рассмеялась.

examples.en: I laughed out loud when I saw him.

examples.en: Hugh laughed heartily at the joke.

examples.en: Frank laughed to cover his anxiety.

examples.en: She laughed away her foolish fears.

examples.en: He threw his head back and laughed.

examples.en: I've never laughed so hard in my life.

examples.en: The children all laughed at his jokes.

examples.en: I laughed so hard I almost wet myself.

examples.en: I laughed at my daughter's monkeyshines.
